 of chemical reactions and may carry detectable life if located\nin a habitable zone. These old planets should be primary targets in search for\nthe extraterrestrial life.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Apr 2014 18:06:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 May 2015 19:30:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2016 07:34:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-24"}
